title: Cossacks 2 - Napoleonic Wars [RTS] ISO x 2
description:
Cossacks 2: Napoleonic Wars.
RTS.
Labelled:- Bink Video/Game World/cdv

Requirements.
1.5GHz CPU.
512 RAM.
98/2000/ME/XP.

Delivered in rar folder contains:-
2 iso files.
1 text document on how to install the game.

Extract the three files from the rar folder, I recommend 7Zip if you havent got an extractor. Get it from the link below.
  <a href="
http://www.filehippo.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://www.filehippo.com/</a>

Once 7Zip has installed, simply right click on the downloaded rar folder and choose EXTRACT HERE.

Two blank writable DVD's are required.
Burn both the iso files onto writable blank DVD's with a iso burner.
Dont burn both the iso's onto one single DVD, two DVD's are required.
Use the DVD's to install and uninstall and play the game.

NOTE:-
This game takes time to load so hang on and be patient.
